CST tool providing the following tools:

1. Key Generation
	- gen_keys
	- gen_drv_drbg
	- gen_otpmk_drbg
2. Header Creation
	- create_hdr_pbi
	- create_hdr_isbc
	- create_hdr_esbc
3. Signature Geneartion
	- sign_img_hash
	- append_sign_hdr

To Sign any image for verification, following tools need to be invoked
1. ./create_hdr_<xxx> <input_file>	(Create the CSF Header with padding added till Signature Offset)
2. ./sign_img_hash <input_file>		(Sign the Image Hash using Private Key)
3. ./append_sign_hdr <input_file>	(Append the signature to end of CSH Header File)

To execute above in a single step, Shell Scripts are provided which would invoke the
required CST Tools
1. sign_pbi.sh
2. sign_isbc.sh
3. sign_esbc.sh

Usage of Scripts:
	./sign_<xxx>.sh <input_file>
